5.1 Prohibited behavior
The following are strictly prohibited on the Platform:
– Publishing illegal content: harassment, incitement to hatred, discriminatory speech, threats, pornographic or violent content;
– Impersonating a third party or creating fictitious accounts;
– Sharing links to malicious, illegal or unauthorized content;
– Attempting to compromise the security of the Platform.

5.2 Moderation system
Ludokan implements hybrid moderation: automatic filters and human review of reports.

5.3 Sanctions
In case of ToU violation: warning, temporary suspension, permanent ban, or reporting to authorities.
